article_title: Paul Davis still a mystery to many Kansas voters
article_text: Paul Davis is not Sam Brownback. That has been a central theme of the Democrat’s campaign. He promises he’ll be different from the guy who currently resides at Cedar Crest. But he’s still a blank slate for many voters, said Bob Beatty, a political science professor at Washburn University.
